 Phobias ship launches from the cybertronian Fire and heads out of 
scanner range. "Computer when we're out of scanner range set the 
coordinates for the Predacon base, and open the frequency we recieved 
from Scourge."

He turned a dial with his left hand and replayed the messages from 
his babies at Magmatrons base, he heard what Magmatron had told 
Shredder about Unicron and the Judge. He hears the message where 
Magmatron said hello to him. (This is not a mode, in one of the 
former posts Magmatron acknowledged Phobia through one of his 
babies.)"What are you up to Magmatron?" he thought as he listened to 
the conversation. He didn't know what to think, was what he said the 
truth, or was the whole story for his benefit?

Those thoughts had to wait, right now he had other priorities.
